data.description: Perfect location close to Lakes, Parks, Highways, Shopping and schools,& a neighborhood pool.Open floorplan. Kitw hdwd flrs, desk, HUGE pantry, access to deck.Tons of windows, Formal dining rm. Up has 4 good size bedrooms, laundry rm,& 3 full baths. Mtr Ste w bthrm w/ dble vanities, lighting, massive closet, jetted tub, & tiled shower. The lower level boasts high ceilings and plenty of space for additional entertaining or working out. If you like boating, swimming, camping, or picnics, you are within walking distance of the local lake!
